# DataInsertable

**Protocol**

A protocol supporting the custom language model training data result builder.

## Declaration

```swift
protocol DataInsertable
```

## Protocol requirements

- **insert(data:)**

## Result builder support

- **SFCustomLanguageModelData.CompoundTemplate**: A class supporting the custom language model training data result builder. You are not intended to use this directly.
- **TemplateInsertable**: A protocol supporting the custom language model training data result builder.

## Conforming Types

- SFCustomLanguageModelData.CustomPronunciation
- SFCustomLanguageModelData.PhraseCount
- SFCustomLanguageModelData.PhraseCountGenerator
- SFCustomLanguageModelData.PhraseCountsFromTemplates
- SFCustomLanguageModelData.TemplatePhraseCountGenerator
